description: This file contains data class definitions for modeling authentication requests/responses and note entities in a notes application.

classes.name: LoginRequest
classes.description: Represents a login request with username and password.

classes.name: LoginResponse
classes.description: Represents a response from login containing an optional token.

classes.name: RegisterRequest
classes.description: Represents a registration request with username and password.

classes.name: RegisterResponse
classes.description: Represents a registration response with an optional message.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: Represents a note with identifiers, content, and timestamps.

classes.name: NoteBody
classes.description: Represents the body of a note, including title and content.
